configset  GLOBAL  site_name = [VALUE]
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
Default Value : [defined during installation]
Data Type     : string
Category      : miscellany
Password Notes: Set with global password. 
= = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = =

EXAMPLE:
configset GLOBAL site_name = Bruno's E-mail Boutique


$INCLUDE-config/site_name

The site_name description can be displayed in many documents and
configuration settings by using the SITE substitution.  
See "help variables" for an introduction to substitution variables.


